@startuml chrispiro_deploy_plotly_app_on_gcp

actor Developer
participant "Local Environment" as Local
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "Google Cloud SDK" as CloudSDK
participant "App Engine" as AppEngine
participant "BigQuery" as BigQuery
participant "Cloud Storage" as CloudStorage

Developer -> Local : Develop Dash app
Developer -> Local : Test locally
Developer -> Git : Commit changes
Developer -> CloudSDK : gcloud app deploy
CloudSDK -> AppEngine : Deploy application
AppEngine -> BigQuery : Query data
AppEngine -> CloudStorage : Fetch data
AppEngine --> Developer : Return deployed app URL

@enduml